name: The Hollows
description:
The Hollows are the bane of any lone dreamer.
While many denizens of the Tapestry pose a danger due to their alien mindset, few show such a clear malice as these massive, shrouded figures.
Like a folktale horror, they scour the Tapestry, hunting down dreamers with vicious dedication, forcing them inside their dark mantles and dragging them into their “cities”, to be sold as if they were mere cattle.
